OL,5, The price of a first class stamp has   
OL,6, risen to #1.25 from #1.10, the third   
OL,7, increase in the space of 18 months.    
OL,9,FRoyal Mail blamed increasing cost      
OL,10,Fpressures and the tough economic       
OL,11,Fenvironment for the latest rise.       
OL,13,FCharity Citizens Advice said that      
OL,14,Fregulator Ofcom should hold the firm to
OL,15,Faccount over "rocketing prices" while  
OL,16,Fhouseholds struggle with rising costs. 
OL,18,FBut Ofcom said pricing "flexibility"   
OL,19,Fwas needed to ensure the postal service
OL,20,Fremained viable.                       
